	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dum haec scripsi, mi <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Bullingere</persName>, quatriduo hęseram in lectulo et corpusculum iam agens annum sexagesimum quintum vix e grabbattulo erexeram et cogor scribere.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quare obsecro, si quid erratum, tu melius interpretare.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hoc oro: Sufficit mihi; tolle, quęso, animam meam.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fiat domini voluntas.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praestantissimo viro domino <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Henrycho Bullingero</persName>, <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tigurino</placeName> theologo, suo domino observando etc.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Zürch.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[Darunter von <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Bullingers</persName> Hand:]</note>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName type="auto_name">Rychenwyler</placeName> enderung.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
